query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng FROM aka_name AS an, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cn.name not like '%Miramax%' AND cn.name not like '%Focus Features%' AND an.name not like '%L%' AND mc.note not like '%Italy%' AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%I%' OR n.name like '%M%' OR n.name like '%U%') AND mi.info in ('Gujarati','Ladino','Georgian','Greek','Arabic') AND (k.keyword like '%betraying%' OR k.keyword like '%identity%')
